rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0001
rows.name:
This strange box...
I see them sometimes when I'm salvaging.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I've always thought they were houses,
but since it's on a road, maybe not?

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0003
rows.name: A dead end...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0005
rows.name: I wonder what lies beyond this.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0004
rows.name:
To think there's such a vast place
so far above Alst... It's incredible.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0101
rows.name:
These weird boxes...
You see them scattered all over Eden.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0102
rows.name: I wonder what they were used for...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0103
rows.name: I guess there's no way past here...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0104
rows.name:
How did people get around
a place this big?

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0201
rows.name:
Mo-mo-mo!
Is this made of iron, Mo-mo?

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0202
rows.name:
No, it's a bit sturdier and lighter...
Fascinating, mo!

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0203
rows.name:
A bit of rubble like this is nothing
for Hana's powerâ€”

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0204
rows.name: ...Or so Tora thought, but Tora will hold back, mo.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0205
rows.name:
There is surely nothing but more rubble waiting
beyond this, mo.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0301
rows.name:
A curious box, but not dissimilar
to the Imperial Army's Cetus...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0302
rows.name: Is this some kind of vehicle?

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0303
rows.name: To dig such a large hole in the rock...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0304
rows.name:
An astounding technology, but I suppose
it could not withstand the weathering of time.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0401
rows.name:
This thing isn't going to start
moving on its own, is it?

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0402
rows.name:
It looks the same as the machines
we saw in the Land of Mors and the World Tree...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0403
rows.name: This is a sturdy wall, just like Teos Aure...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0404
rows.name:
But even if we got past it, I'm sure there'd be
nothing but the same desolate scenery
waiting for us...
